The TODO App 
--It is used to keep track my tasks so that I won't miss one.
--I have used HTML,CSS and JavaScript for this App.
--It is a desktop environment based App.
--I have used firebase as a backend database.
--I have incorporated functionalities like
      --Add task
      --Delete task
      --Mark task as completed
      --View All tasks
      --View Completed tasks
      --View Pending tasks
      --Clear Completed tasks
      --Clear All tasks
 --If the tasks are not displayed properly, please click on completed or pending options once.
 --Applying changes might not be instantaneous because of responses are being brought from the firebase server.It also depends on the Internet speed.
